{"title":"Panorama Cycles Updates the Anticosti Adventure Gravel Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/panorama-cycles-updates-the-anticosti-adventure-gravel-bike/","date":1742830380000,"content":"<p><em>With its comfortable geometry, lightweight tubing selection and excellent tire clearance, the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/panorama-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Panorama Cycles</a> Anticosti is created for long <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/adventure-gravel-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">adventure gravel</a> riding and lightweight touring. Read on for all the featured updates…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-05.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-05.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-05.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-05.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-06.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-06.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-06.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-06.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-04.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-04.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Anticosti has undergone a complete chassis redo, with an increase in tire clearance to 2.1″ 29er tires, internal cable routing for the dropper seatpost and UDH, and a custom selection of Reynolds 725 steel tubing for each of the 5 frame sizes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-07.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-07.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-07.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-07.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>The Reynolds steel chassis is now available in carbon or steel fork configurations. This means you can optimize the bike’s weight and performance or choose a fork that fits every rack on the market.</em></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-01.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-01.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-08.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-08.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-08.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-08.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Anticosti Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Frameset $1399 Complete build as shown $3,249</li>\n<li>A custom selection of Reynolds steel tubes for each of the five frame sizes.</li>\n<li>New: choice of carbon or steel fork. Versatility for gravel or light touring.</li>\n<li>UDH standard. T-Type transmission ready</li>\n<li>Clearance increase for 29 x 2.1″ tires</li>\n<li>Dropper seatpost and dynamo hub compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_Geo.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_Geo.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_Geo.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_Geo.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-09.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-09.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-09.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-09.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-10.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-10.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-10.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Panorama_Anticosti_Gravel_-10.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>The Anticosti is now available for pre-order on the website <a href=\"https://www.panoramacycles.com/products/anticosti-3\" target=\"_blank\">www.panoramacycles.com</a> and at retailers, with delivery expected starting May 2025. The bike will be available as a frame/fork set (1699$ CAD/$1399 USD) or as a complete bike starting at $3,949 CAD ($3,249 USD).</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/panorama-cycles-updates-the-anticosti-adventure-gravel-bike/\">Panorama Cycles Updates the Anticosti Adventure Gravel Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"91b1301325decce3cab0bb0b89c030bbf210238f1281ceeb6803399b1615ec6c","category":"Cycling"}